Place all ingredients except chops in saucepan. Bring to boil; reduce heat to low. Simmer 10 minutes, stirring occasionally. Place chops on greased grill over medium coals; brush generously with barbecue sauce mixture. Cover. Grill 15 minutes. Turn; brush with barbecue sauce mixture. Continue grilling, covered, 10 to 15 minutes or until chops are cooked through.